</title>
<subSubSection id="E2E4FFAEA5A48DAAAC8B6867D3ADA44F" pageId="null" pageNumber="183" type="description">
<paragraph id="2CE91B3D280FDE78920CE7702814D299" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<emphasis id="7A27C8974301C00CFBA2778E53A51085" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
B. 
<taxonomicName id="ABDCB3868502232206CCAF9CC8796263" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Brassicaceae" genus="Erucastrum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Brassicales" pageId="null" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Erucastrum</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Nr. 1) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="19BF4CCD9B3A7884C55A09FFF8D3CEDB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<normalizedToken id="71645E8CFE3C517CBF46ED12F5DE203C" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
jederseits mit 5-9 Abschnitten; 
<normalizedToken id="F1CD2EFDA6069E0B20D6D323BA186761" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
⅓- 
<normalizedToken id="59319D92C0679C83E3DB9A09542F9CED" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="B68F8073D2429294920B408F2879C601" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="53886ADA816BB3DE35C81E3E685BD1B6" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="1691EED782202E91ADDBF03DB036FCEB" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
10-12 mm lang; 
<normalizedToken id="10915F73C84332C7DFF2EC5B75BBEA42" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
20-25 mm lang;
</emphasis>
Fruchtstiele 3 
<emphasis id="6456124629E8ED8034DF696A91B9C44E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">-</emphasis>
8 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="599A21E515E2DC7F60F2928DB9C7B05B" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3870BCD3DE489477B9E8091A2F57904C" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="7D4C1EC65C370F37434A4F33431F9269" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="11126C725F3EDBBF2933533A8CE1563A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">24:</emphasis>
Material aus den Bergamasker Alpen (Val Brembana) (Favarger 1965), aus den 
<normalizedToken id="73D1CC31703B168C98D87AB8E0EF7DAC" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="34154037EC95E465C552196D1E135A21" originalValue="Küpfer" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Kuepfer</normalizedToken>
1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9FF8F920641A467F6E765790E79C053F" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="5869120E70F282D56EC8287D40CA9D80" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Ziemlich feuchte, lockere, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="523EE9ACF66707EFACD11957C7CF8EE4" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in 
<normalizedToken id="DC0995C2D079A7814B5B6D64001DC855" originalValue="Südlagen" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Suedlagen</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="72DA413083723FA11B723415B4CC7E86" originalValue="Schutthänge" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Schutthaenge</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="8B529E7B68066E7C2215C30DFD38A56A" originalValue="Aufschüttungen" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Aufschuettungen</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F7B4FB4F25A2B8BF7AFE44A5D725998F" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
<emphasis id="3EDDEB9009F79F2700FDD9A59B1C8AE9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="0B50F4E2F1F07BE7EBA82344C8BB1AF6" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="D4BF1DC8058EA4DA0186E89FCA2C482A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">westlich</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="09B4C5C27D6E3BB414D7F13E57133117" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">:</emphasis>
Nordspanische Gebirge, 
<normalizedToken id="4A4EB5FA05E2499640AD1C53108871CF" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Plateau Central (Cantal, 
<normalizedToken id="B83AEC8018E83FD3C2FE32C6C903DE51" originalValue="Lozère" pageId="null" pageNumber="183">Lozere</normalizedToken>
), Westalpen (Alpes Maritimes bis Bergamasker Alpen), mittlerer Apennin. Apuanische Alpen, Korsika, Sardinien. - Im Gebiet: Grajische Alpen (Gebiet von Cogne), Valsesia (Sabbia, Alpe Cevia), Bergamasker Alpen (oberstes Val Brembana).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
